---
import GlobalLayout from "../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
---

<GlobalLayout class:list={["bg-white"]}>
    <section class="flex flex-col items-center py-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[Noto_Serif_Display] text-[#004346] mb-10">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 text-[#004346] text-left space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
            <p>We collect personal information (name, delivery address, phone number, email, payment details) to process your orders and improve our service. We use your contact information to send order confirmations, delivery updates, and important notices. We may also use anonymized data to analyze trends and optimize the app.</p>
            <p>All payment information is handled securely. We use encryption and trusted payment gateways, ensuring your data is not exposed. We will never use your financial information for any purpose other than processing your order.</p>
            <p>We will not sell your personal data. We share necessary data only with service providers (e.g. payment processors, delivery partners) to fulfill orders, and as required by law.</p>
            <p>We may use cookies or similar technologies in the app to remember your preferences and improve functionality. You can disable non-essential cookies in your device settings, but this may affect some features.</p>
            <p>Daily Bazzar is committed to protecting your privacy and keeping your data secure.</p>
            <p>We may update these terms and policies at any time. Any changes will be posted in the app and take effect immediately. We encourage you to review the terms periodically.</p>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@dailybazzar.com" class="text-[#0094BD] underline">admin@dailybazzar.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</GlobalLayout> 